arricades a voice was heard in the heads of all the defenders. \"I am Overlord Ralakor of Belrow. The nation of the dead. Long ago, we where forced to destroy the living. We shall not allow this to pass again. No more lives will be lost because of the evil use of the dead. No more innocent blood spilt.\"", "link_list": [], "image_list": ["https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/2c/fa/87/2cfa87b68ac21f4ba6f25f3ce2f4aacf.jpg"], "html": "In the darkness of the night a sound could be heard in the far distance. The sounds of thousands of feet marching in unison. At first all that could be seen was two faint green lights in the fair distance. These lights soon got larger and larger and shapes began to form. Two massive pyramid structures moved towards the city. On lookers would slowly see that other shapes where beginning to form in front of these massive black monoliths. "}, "post-37150": {"user": "Lady Nyx \"The Kingslayer\" Mann", "user_num": 503, "timestamp": "1462860641000", "message": "From her post atop the fortifications she saw the Land Tillers first. As she had been fighting with cavalry for sometime she was impressed by their force. She responed to Raynor, \"Aye, and it is most welcome. We have managed to hold the undead back but it was only a matter of time before they overwhelmed us. Your timing couldn't have been better.\" At this point a soldier came and whispered in the Queen's ear. The news troubled her greatly. She marched quickly from her post and went to meet this new undead arriving. ", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "From her post atop the fortifications she saw the Land Tillers first. As she had been fighting with cavalry for sometime she was impressed by their force. She responed to Raynor, \"Aye, and it is most welcome. We have managed to hold the undead back but it was only a matter of time before they overwhelmed us. Your timing couldn't have been better.\" "}, "post-37151": {"user": null, "user_num": null, "timestamp": "1462860817000", "message": "The rear guard of the 3rd Legion quickly formed a defensive line against the approaching forces of Berlow. With their city having been taken by undead, the soldiers saw these new forces as more enemies and were readying for a fight they would surely loose. When the leader of their army spoke the forces of the 3rd made no reply. They would wait for the queen. ", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "The rear guard of the 3rd Legion quickly formed a defensive line against the approaching forces of Berlow. With their city having been taken by undead, the soldiers saw these new forces as more enemies and were readying for a fight they would surely loose. When the leader of their army spoke the forces of the 3rd made no reply. They would wait for the queen. "}, "post-37152": {"user": "Lady Nyx \"The Kingslayer\" Mann", "user_num": 503, "timestamp": "1462861179000", "message": "They would not have to wait long. Nyx arrived very hastily. She had heard the words of Ralakor but she knew her soldiers would still be mistrusting against them. She broke through the 3rd Legion's lines and greeted the undead herself. \"I am Nyx Mann, Queen of Aaedan. If you truly seek to help put down the evil in our home, you are welcome. My soldiers are wary of your kind, as they have been fighting undead for days. Forgive them for their mistrust.\" ", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "They would not have to wait long. Nyx arrived very hastily. She had heard the words of Ralakor but she knew her soldiers would still be mistrusting against them. She broke through the 3rd Legion's lines and greeted the undead herself. \"I am Nyx Mann, Queen of Aaedan. If you truly seek to help put down the evil in our home, you are welcome. My soldiers are wary of your kind, as they have been fighting undead for days. Forgive them for their mistrust.\" "}, "post-37154": {"user": null, "user_num": null, "timestamp": "1462861629000", "message": "Thunder boomed overhead, the tower of